OL,4,BVAR: Mike Riley tells Premier League
OL,5,Bclub 'improvement is required'
OL,6, Referees' chief Mike Riley has told
OL,7, Premier League clubs that "improvement
OL,8, is required" with the video assistant
OL,9, referee system.
OL,11,FThe technology has caused frustration
OL,12,Fand controversy since its introduction
OL,13,Fat the start of the season.
OL,15,FAt a meeting on Thursday, Riley gave a
OL,16,Ffull appraisal of VAR with clubs
OL,17,Fdiscussing their "grave concerns".
OL,19,FThe Premier League has promised to
OL,20,Fimprove VAR's consistency and speed and
OL,21,Fincrease communication with fans.
